       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. GRAPHICS-DERIVATIVES.
       
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. VULKAN-FRAGMENT-SHADER.

       DATA DIVISION.
       INPUT SECTION.
       01 IN-COLOR PIC V(4) LOCATION 0.
       
       OUTPUT SECTION.
       01 OUT-COLOR PIC V(4) LOCATION 0.

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 DX PIC V(4).
       01 DY PIC V(4).
       01 FW PIC V(4).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
           CALL "DERIVATIVE-X" USING IN-COLOR GIVING DX.
           CALL "DERIVATIVE-Y" USING IN-COLOR GIVING DY.
           CALL "TOTAL-DERIVATIVE" USING IN-COLOR GIVING FW.
           
           COMPUTE OUT-COLOR = DX + DY + FW.
           GOBACK.
